                  <p>Includes a 1827 manuscript transcription of the will of Baron de Bastrop; land grants for territory in San Felipe de Austin, San Antonio de Bexar, and the Matagorda League; correspondence concerning land allocations; financial records concerning the Austin family's finances; a 1843 letter to Santa Anna concerning a plan to make peace with the Texans; and a 1831 manuscript petition from Hosea H. League and Seth Ingram to be released from the San Felipe de Austin jail.</p>
